{
  "description": "Validated 3-bet charts for 6-max cash. Based on GTO Wizard benchmarks and Modern Poker Theory (Acevedo 2019). Key correction: 3-bet bluffs should be wheel aces (A2s-A5s) and similar blockers — NOT suited connectors. Suited connectors (T9s, 98s, JTs, etc.) belong in the call range because they have strong implied odds and equity realization when flatting, not as 3-bet bluffs. Bluff:Value ratio target ~1:2 to 1:2.5. Version: 2.0.",
